data.description: This charming home boasts a generous 2,680 square feet of living space, providing room for family, friends, and more. The spacious and well-lit living areas are highlighted by the gleaming hardwood floors on the upper level, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance.  Step into the backyard oasis, featuring a brand-new above-ground pool - an ideal spot to unwind and entertain during warm summer days. The fresh landscaping adds to the property's curb appeal, creating a visually stunning environment.  This home is nestled in a quiet neighborhood, offering a serene and peaceful atmosphere. Whether you're enjoying the private backyard or taking a stroll around the block, you'll relish the tranquility of this location.
